# Installation of GHC 7.8.3

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution
cd $HOME/Downloads

wget https://www.haskell.org/ghc/dist/7.8.3/ghc-7.8.3-x86_64-unknown-linux-deb7.tar.bz2
tar xvfj ghc-7.8.3-x86_64-unknown-linux-deb7.tar.bz2

cd ghc-7.8.3

# install to
mkdir $HOME/Software/ghc-7.8.3

./configure --prefix=$HOME/Software/ghc-7.8.3
make install

# remove temporary files
cd $HOME/Downloads
rm -rfv ghc-7.8.3*
~~~

## Activation Script

~~~
cd $HOME/GHC-compiler/bin
rm -f ghc
ln -s `pwd`/ghc-7.8.3 ghc  
~~~
